nodes.text: Forest of Endor Log Cake is a real-world cake recipe in the 2021 book Star Wars: Galactic Baking, which was released for Star Wars Day. The cake's appearance was inspired by Endor. Its ingredients are eggs, vegetable oil, unsweetened dark cocoa powder, baking powder, vanilla extract, granulated sugar, powdered sugar, egg whites, tartar, chocolate chips or chocolate candy covering, green candy melts, cream cheese, matcha powder, and whipped topping.
